) was a good idea.=A0 Problem is, there's plenty of electricity being waste=
d in the process.=A0 It seems to me that it should be possible to develop s=
ome sort of use for this dedicated CPU effort.=A0 What's a major use of CPU=
 power?=A0 One is weather forecasting, another is simulations of various ki=
nds.=A0 These use huge amounts of computer-time, and if they are made to be=
 sufficiently divisible people could earn digital-coin by doing things that=
 are actually valuable in and of themselves.=0A=0A=A0=A0=A0 Jim Bell=0A=0A=
